title: Battle of #Memes - Polygon
body:
Select your favorite three picks from the below list of submitted memes. At the end of voting, the top three selections will be awarded 1st-3rd place based on their total votes received.

All $APW and $MATIC holders at the time of snapshot are eligible for this vote.

See the Medium post about contest rules and submissions:

https://apwine.medium.com/let-the-defi-decathlon-begin-ten-days-of-meme-events-753910fb61f2
